doctype html
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        title Privacy Policy | Lior Maman
        //- בהנחה שאתה משתמש ב-Bootstrap בפורטפוליו
        link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css")
        style.
            body { background-color: #1f1f1f; color: #fff; font-family: sans-serif; }
            .policy-container { max-width: 800px; margin: 80px auto; padding: 40px; background: #2a2a2a; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
            h1 { color: #00adb5; margin-bottom: 30px; }
            h3 { color: #eee; margin-top: 25px; font-size: 1.3rem; }
            p, li { color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; }
            hr { border-color: #444; margin: 30px 0; }

    body
        .container
            .policy-container
                h1 Privacy Policy
                p.text-muted Effective Date: June 7, 2026

                p Welcome to the personal portfolio website of Lior Maman. This website serves strictly as a professional portfolio and a testing ground for experimental software concepts ("Beta Services"). By using this site, you agree to the terms outlined below.

                hr

                h3 1. "As-Is" & Beta Status
                p This website is operated as a personal portfolio project and is **not a registered business entity**. All interactive features are provided strictly as a free-trial, anonymous, and experimental Beta version. Services are provided on an **"AS-IS"** basis without any warranties.

                h3 2. No User Accounts & Data Minimization
                p To ensure your privacy, **we do not create user accounts, manage profiles, or store personal identity data in our database.**
                ul
                    li #[strong Session Inputs:] Text prompts or configurations you input are processed in real-time to generate demo results and are not linked to your personal identity.
                    li #[strong Server Logs:] Anonymous technical data (like browser type or timestamps) may be processed temporarily by our hosting provider for security and debugging.

                h3 3. Third-Party APIs
                p This site may interact with third-party APIs (such as AI engines or payment UI simulators) to display technical features. Data entered is transmitted temporarily to these providers for real-time processing. Please do not submit sensitive or proprietary data.

                h3 4. Cookies & Local Storage
                p We use basic browser local storage or cookies strictly for core technical functionalities (such as keeping track of your session layout preferences). We do not use marketing or tracking cookies.

                h3 5. Limitation of Liability
                p Lior Maman shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, or consequential damages, including loss of data or system downtime, arising from your use of these experimental portfolio features.

                h3 6. Contact
                p For any questions regarding this policy or the portfolio, you can reach out directly via the contact methods provided on the main page.
        script(src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js")